    <h1>Bullying isn't cool!</h1>
    <p>Bullying is defined as the use of superior strength or influence to intimidate someone. It can damage people's self esteem and confidence in a very harsh way. Although bullying is acknowledged it can be hard to find the courage to report it. We should begin to take a step forward to become upstanders instead of bystanders.</p>
  </div>
